        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Wizards who choose to become abjurers specialize in spells from the school of abjuration. Abjurers are best known as the foremost experts with defensive spells, but they are also talented at blocking the spells of other spellcasters. Abjurers are often employed as bodyguards or support for military organizations.</p><p></p><table class=\"features-table\" data-toc-level=\"3\" style=\"text-align:left\"><caption style=\"text-align:center\">The Abjurer</caption><colgroup><col class=\"level\" style=\"text-align:left\"></col><col class=\"features\" style=\"text-align:left\"></col></colgroup><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\"text-align:left\">Level</th><th scope=\"col\" style=\"text-align:left\">Features</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"level\">1</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.4ZBZTsb96tSV1xaX]{Abjuration Specialist}, Bonus Spells: @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.3fVnKST3p10nK5v1]{Mage Armor}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.k6lJOHWJa0XF2zCb]{Shield}</td></tr><tr><td class=\"level\">3</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.lR3mHLH9J3pCK9wZ]{Greater Mage Armor}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.rf5y6WC05YGp7dHu]{Reactive Barrier}</td></tr><tr><td class=\"level\">6</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.0x5BtKkD4O4STmXr]{Counterspell}</td></tr><tr><td class=\"level\">10</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.5wTi1HbWOVnuAp83]{Abjurer's Ward}</td></tr><tr><td class=\"level\">14</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.0x5BtKkD4O4STmXr]{Counterspell}</td></tr></tbody></table>",
